print("hello\rindia") #india


identifier
______________
it is user defined word.
This word is used to give name of the variable clasname ,.....

rule
______
(1)it consist of
 a to z
A to Z
0 to 9
_

(2)not start with digit

(3)space not allow
(4)case senistive  a!=A
(5) predefined word not allow

